{"tid":216633,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"換天花燈","createTime":"2017-04-25T10:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T10:23:24.000Z","uid":7283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76970ec93f82df8eab0330f1b78700d82adf8fb5","tid":216633,"uid":7283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"首先認昂鳩先<br />\n因為拆之前唔記得影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天花個窿有4條線（2組）如下圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4To9W6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4To9W6Q.jpg&h=b8797341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑色果組係扭埋一齊所以應該唔會錯<br />\n宜家將紅色同兩條黑色駁左落盞燈度<br />\n著到冇問題<br />\n但變左附近另一盞壁燈著唔到<br />\n懷疑係關冇駁果條黑色事<br />\n想請教應該點駁 <br />\n唔該晒"}]}